tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  distance FLOAT NOT NULL,
  traffic_conditions VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  estimated_delivery_time TIME NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE traffic_data (
 traffic_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 order_id UUID,
 current_traffic_level INT,
 traffic_conditions TEXT,
 traffic_time_estimation TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    distance FLOAT,
    traffic_conditions TEXT,
    estimated_delivery_time TIMESTAMP
);
